languages.text: "Еще нет". {n}Кривая ухмылка ложится на каменное лицо.{/n} "В портовом терминале мы нашли кое-что... Сразу за десятинным судном отбыл один подозрительный корабль. Я уже знаю, как его выследить".

"Not yet, it hasn't." {n}A crooked smile crosses his face.{/n} "We did find something on the port terminal... Shortly after the tithe was hauled away, a suspicious ship took off from the planet. And I already know how to track it down."

languages.text: « Non, pas tout à fait, {n}dit-il en affichant un sourire en coin.{/n} Nous avons découvert quelque chose dans le terminal de l'astroport... Un vaisseau suspect a décollé de la planète peu après le départ de la dîme. Et je sais déjà comment le retrouver. »
languages.original_text: "Not yet, it hasn't." {n}A crooked smile crosses his face.{/n} "We did find something on the port terminal... Shortly after the tithe was hauled away, a suspicious ship took off from the planet. And I already know how to track it down."

languages.text: «No, todavía no». {n}Su rostro esboza una torva sonrisa.{/n} «Algo hemos descubierto en el terminal del puerto... Al poco de sustraerse el diezmo, una nave sospechosa despegó del planeta. Y sé bien cómo seguirle el rastro».
languages.original_text: "Not yet, it hasn't." {n}A crooked smile crosses his face.{/n} "We did find something on the port terminal... Shortly after the tithe was hauled away, a suspicious ship took off from the planet. And I already know how to track it down."

languages.text: “没有，还没有。”{n}他的脸上掠过一丝狡黠的笑容。{/n}“我们确实在星港的码头附近发现了一些东西……满载什一税的货船起飞后不久，一艘可疑的船就离开了这颗行星。而且，我已经弄清了那艘船的下落。”

languages.text: 「まだです。まだ終わっていません」{n}彼の顔にゆがんだ笑みが浮かんだ。{/n}「港のターミナルで、あるものを見つけました…租税が運び出された直後に、怪しい船がこの惑星から飛び立ちました。そして、その船を追跡する手段も、もうわかっています」
